       s.hull  computes  the  convex  hull of a sites list and outputs it in a
       binary vector file (vect).



OOPPTTIIOONNSS
   FFllaaggss::
       --aa     Use all sites found in the named sites file, rather than  limit-
              ing  output  to  sites  falling  within  the  current geographic
              region.

       --ss     Automatically run "v.support" on newly created vector file.


   PPaarraammeetteerrss::
